<button class="mt-2 text-xs underline text-slate-600">Show data table (the chart as a table)</button>
<div class="mt-2 flex items-end gap-2 flex-wrap">
<span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Add ORF benchmark:</span>
<label class="text-xs text-slate-600 flex flex-col">Grade<input type="number" class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border rounded" value=""/>
</label>
<label class="text-xs text-slate-600 flex flex-col">Season<select class="px-2 py-1 border rounded">
<option value="fall">fall</option>
<option value="winter" selected="">winter</option>
<option value="spring">spring</option>
</select>
</label>
<button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded border border-teal-600 text-teal-700 hover:bg-teal-50">Add</button>
</div>
<div class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
<span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Export this view:</span>
<button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded border border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50">Brief (HTML)</button>
<button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded border border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50">Data (CSV)</button>
<label class="text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-1">
<input type="checkbox"/>Include identifiable data (FERPA)</label>
</div>
<div class="mt-3 p-3 rounded-lg" style="background:#0a1f2e;border:1px solid #0891b2;color:#e8f0f5">
<h4 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider mb-1" style="color:#22d3ee">🔬 Evidence Inquiry — Should I Trust This Trend?</h4>
<p class="text-[10px] opacity-85 mb-2 leading-snug">Set trend strength, sample size, baseline, and AI ladder level. Predict where the evidence sits between insufficient and over-interpreted. No score, no reveal.</p>
<div class="inline-block px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold mb-2" style="background:#22d3ee;color:#000">Suggestive · slope/noise 0.41</div>
<p class="text-[10px] opacity-80 mb-2">Pattern hints at change but could be noise. Useful for generating hypotheses, weak for action.</p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mb-2">
<label class="text-[10px]">
<div class="flex justify-between mb-0.5">
<span>Trend strength</span>
<span class="font-mono font-bold" style="color:#22d3ee">0.50</span>
</div>
<input type="range" min="0" max="2" step="0.05" class="w-full" value="0.5"/>
</label>
<label class="text-[10px]">
<div class="flex justify-between mb-0.5">
<span>Observations</span>
<span class="font-mono font-bold" style="color:#22d3ee">8</span>
</div>
<input type="range" min="2" max="40" step="1" class="w-full" value="8"/>
</label>
<label class="text-[10px]">
<div class="flex justify-between mb-0.5">
<span>Baseline value</span>
<span class="font-mono font-bold" style="color:#22d3ee">50</span>
</div>
<input type="range" min="0" max="200" step="1" class="w-full" value="50"/>
</label>
<label class="text-[10px]">
<div class="flex justify-between mb-0.5">
<span>AI ladder (L0-L3)</span>
<span class="font-mono font-bold" style="color:#22d3ee">L1</span>
</div>
<input type="range" min="0" max="3" step="1" class="w-full" value="1"/>
</label>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-2 mb-2">
<button class="flex-1 px-2 py-1 rounded text-[10px] font-bold" style="background:#0a1f2e;color:#22d3ee;border:1px solid #0891b2;cursor:pointer">📋 Log this evidence call</button>
<button class="px-2 py-1 rounded text-[10px]" style="background:#0a0a1a;color:#94a3b8;border:1px solid #1e293b;cursor:pointer">Reset</button>
</div>
<label class="block text-[10px] font-bold opacity-85 mb-1">Your hypothesis (when does dialing AI up start to mislead, and what guard would you add?)</label>
<textarea rows="2" placeholder="e.g., past L2 you need to surface the slope/noise ratio so the AI cannot manufacture certainty..." class="w-full p-1.5 rounded text-[10px] mb-2" style="background:#0a0a1a;border:1px solid #0891b2;color:#e8f0f5;resize:vertical">
</textarea>
<button class="px-2 py-1 rounded text-[10px] font-bold mb-2" style="background:#0a0a1a;color:#22d3ee;border:1px solid #1e293b;cursor:pointer">🤔 I&#x27;m stuck — show open questions</button>
<label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-bold cursor-pointer mb-1">
<input type="checkbox"/>
<span>I can explain why this evidence configuration yields this evidentiary state.</span>
</label>
<p class="m-0 text-[9px] italic opacity-60">Inquiry widget — no score, no reveal. Slope-to-noise is a heuristic; formal claims should use seasonal benchmarks, growth norms, and progress-monitoring decision rules (Deno, Fuchs).</p>
</div>
<p class="mt-3 text-[10px] text-slate-400">Phase 1 — L1 default fires zero AI; dial up for gated, marked AI. Exports are FERPA-gated (identifiable CSV is opt-in) and IEP-team exports require sign-off on any AI reading. docs/lumen_design.md.</p>
</div>"
`;

